          >
          </div>
          <time class="mb-1 text-xl font-bold leading-none text-font-color md:text-2xl">2017 - 2018</time>
          <h4 class="timeline-title text-md font-regular text-font-color dark:text-white md:text-xl">
            Advertisement distributor at FK Distribution A/S
          </h4>
        </li>
        <li class="mb-16 ms-4">
          <div
            class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-font-color rounded-full mt-1.5 -start-1.5 border border-font-color dark:border-font-color dark:bg-font-color"
