          </div>
          <time class="mb-1 text-xl font-bold leading-none text-font-color md:text-2xl">August 2018 - June 2019</time>
          <h4 class="timeline-title text-md font-regular text-font-color dark:text-white md:text-xl">10th grade at Egeskolen</h4>
        </li>
        <li class="mb-16 ms-4">
