          <h4 class="timeline-title text-md font-regular text-font-color md:text-xl">Assistant in webshop in Lloyd Concept Store CPH</h4>
          <p class="text-[#acacac] md:text-lg text-sm">
            * Went on a 6-month leave during my time there, <br class="md:hidden block" /> due to my stay at Bosei (folk high school)
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="mb-16 ms-4">
          <div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-font-color rounded-full mt-1.5 -start-1.5 border border-font-color dark:border-font-color dark:bg-gray-300">
          </div>
          <time class="mb-1 text-xl font-bold leading-none text-font-color md:text-2xl">January 2022 - June 2022 (gap-year)</time>
          <h4 class="timeline-title text-md font-regular text-font-color md:text-xl">
            Folk high school stay at Bosei Sports <br class="md:hidden block" /> Folk High School
          </h4>
        </li>
        <li class="mb-16 ms-4">
          <div
            class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-font-color rounded-full mt-1.5 -start-1.5 border border-font-color dark:border-font-color dark:bg-font-color"
          >
          </div>
          <time class="mb-1 text-xl font-bold leading-none text-font-color md:text-2xl">August 2022 - May 2023</time>
          <h4 class="timeline-title text-md font-regular text-font-color md:text-xl">
            Singular courses in History (dropped)* <br class="md:hidden block" /> & Japanese (lvl. 0-B) at Frederiksberg VUC & STX
          </h4>
          <p class="text-[#acacac] md:text-lg text-sm">*Had to drop it due to work & just continue with one course</p>
        </li>
        <li class="mb-16 ms-4">
          <div
            class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-font-color rounded-full mt-1.5 -start-1.5 border border-font-color dark:border-font-color dark:bg-font-color"
          >
          </div>
          <time class="mb-1 text-xl font-bold leading-none text-font-color md:text-2xl">August 2023 - present</time>
          <h4 class="timeline-title text-md font-regular text-font-color dark:text-white md:text-xl">
            Multimedia-design student at <br class="md:hidden block" /> KEA - Københavns Erhvervsakademi (4th and final semester)
          </h4>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </div>

